Package: datastreamr.helper
Title: A Helper Package for datastreamr, the R Wrapper for DataStream's Public API
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Patrick", "Schaefer", , "patrick@datastream.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package helps users make calls to DataStream's public API through datastreamr.
    It allows users to specify inputs to the API using standard R operators and formats (i.e., lists and vectors).
    It also validates user inputs to `select` and `filter` for each endpoint, and validates some
    lookup values.
